{
  "_comment": [
    "Interface/direction data for profile P3 (p3_agra_core_mms.json),",
    "parsed row-by-row from Table 3-1 ('MMS for MA L1 Interfaces') of",
    "ref/a-gra-main/Documentation/ASK 5.0a MA L1 Compliance Document.pdf",
    "and resolved to XSD global element names against the pinned",
    "agra_5_0a drop, exactly as the profile's root list was (see the",
    "manifest's _comment and pim/uci_profiles/README.md, 'P3",
    "conversion-scope decision').",
    "",
    "Structure: interfaces.<IFACE>.<element> = direction, where IFACE is",
    "one of the compliance document's four interface columns (C2, MS,",
    "P2P, VI) and direction is the table's Direction cell verbatim.",
    "Direction is relative to the interface's far side (the C2 station,",
    "mission system, peer, or vehicle -- NOT the Mission Autonomy",
    "system): 'in' means the far side receives the message (the MA",
    "system sends/publishes it), 'out' means the far side sends it (the",
    "MA system receives/subscribes), 'inout' means both. Checked",
    "against known flows: MA_ActionCommand is C2 'out' (the C2 station",
    "commands, MA executes) and MA_FlightCommand is VI 'in' (MA",
    "commands the vehicle).",
    "",
    "The table's MUC (Mission Use Case) column is deliberately not",
    "carried: profile P3 converts every row regardless of MUC tag, so",
    "the tag does not affect anything generated from this file. Row",
    "counts per interface: C2 262, MS 114, P2P 243, VI 49 (668 rows,",
    "343 unique messages -- the union equals the manifest's roots,",
    "test-guarded). These are direct row counts and differ from the",
    "approximate per-interface numbers in",
    "doc/research/AME/a_gra_standard_review.md section 6.2, which were",
    "derived from the document's summary arithmetic, not a row parse.",
    "",
    "Consumed by pim/gen_interaction_seam.py to derive the",
    "pim/agra_p3_seam/ service protos. Do not edit by hand except to",
    "correct a mis-parsed row against the PDF itself."
  ],
